  <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1" facs="../images/ew_b5_1652_001.jpg"/>
         <div>
         <head>
            <date when="1930-07-21">7 = 21 = 1930 <name type="person">miss <choice><abbr>Em</abbr><expan>Eartha M.</expan></choice> White</name></date><lb/>
         </head>
         <p>
            Dear madam<choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice> Just<lb/>
            a few Lines to ask<lb/>
            ya to see if I can get<lb/>
            some aid from ya<lb/>
            and to <supplied reason="illegible" cert="high">Explain</supplied> the<lb/>
            matters to ya that is<lb/>
            this now <name type="person"><choice><sic>mis</sic><corr>miss</corr></choice> White</name> <choice><sic>sence</sic><corr>since</corr></choice><lb/>
            i have <choice><sic>Be</sic><corr>been</corr></choice> in here there has<lb/>
            <choice><sic>Ben</sic><corr>been</corr></choice> something <choice><sic>hapen</sic><corr>happen</corr></choice> to<lb/>
            my <choice><sic>oldes</sic><corr>oldest</corr></choice> Daughter<choice><orig/><reg>,</reg></choice> and I<lb/>
            want to see if ya could<lb/>
            help get her in the<lb/>
            <choice><sic>hosPittle</sic><corr>hospital</corr></choice><choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice> if so i will <choice><sic>apreashete</sic><corr>appreciate</corr></choice><lb/>
            it very much now <choice><orig/><reg>,</reg></choice><name type="person">mrs<lb/>
               White</name><choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice> i have <choice><sic>Ben</sic><corr>been</corr></choice> <choice><sic>struglin</sic><corr>struggling</corr></choice><lb/>
         </p>
         </div>
         <pb/>
         <div>
         <head>2</head>
         <p>
            with them <choice><sic>Every</sic><corr>ever</corr></choice> <choice><sic>sence</sic><corr>since</corr></choice><lb/>
            their mother Died and<lb/>
            had no help with them<lb/>
            <choice><sic>untill</sic><corr>until</corr></choice> this Last past<lb/>
            six months<choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice> my mother<lb/>
            had them for a while<lb/>
            and my sister in laws<lb/>
            went and got them<choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice><lb/>
            they kept them about<lb/>
            <supplied reason="illegible" cert="high">four</supplied> weeks<choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice> i Bought<lb/>
            <choice><sic>grociers</sic><corr>groceries</corr></choice> and<lb/>
            Payed Rent for all<lb/>
            of them to stay and<lb/>
            they got mad with<lb/>
            me <choice><sic>Becarse</sic><corr>because</corr></choice> i would<lb/>
            not Let her have<lb/>
         </p>
         </div>
         <pb n="2" facs="../images/ew_b5_1652_002.jpg"/>
         <div>
         <p>
            fifteen Dollars to <choice><sic>By</sic><corr>buy</corr></choice><lb/>
            her man some<lb/>
            <choice><sic>cloths</sic><corr>clothes</corr></choice> and they put<lb/>
            my kids out in<lb/>
            the street <supplied reason="illegible" cert="medium">at 15 <choice><sic>octock</sic><corr>o'clock</corr></choice></supplied><lb/>
            at night and they<lb/>
            came <supplied reason="illegible" cert="medium"><choice><sic>throu</sic><corr>through</corr></choice></supplied> the street<lb/>
            Looking for me<choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice> so they<lb/>
            went to a friend<lb/>
            of mine house<choice><orig/><reg>,</reg></choice> and<lb/>
            she gave them<lb/>
            a Place to stay<choice><orig/><reg>,</reg></choice> and<lb/>
            she has <choice><orig>all ways</orig><reg>always</reg></choice> cared<lb/>
            for my kids<choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice> <choice><sic>no</sic><corr>now</corr></choice> my sisters<lb/>
            <supplied reason="omitted-in-original">in</supplied>laws want them again<choice><orig/><reg>,</reg></choice><lb/>
            and i <choice><orig>Dont</orig><reg>don't</reg></choice> want them
         </p>
         </div>
         <pb/>
            <div>
               <head>4</head>
               <p>
                  to have them <choice><sic>Becarse</sic><corr>because</corr></choice><lb/>
                  they are not the Right<lb/>
                  wi<gap reason="illegible"/>er to have them<choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice><lb/>
                  they have never <choice><sic>Don</sic><corr>done</corr></choice><lb/>
                  anything for them at<lb/>
                  all so they <supplied reason="illegible" cert="medium">wont</supplied> Let<lb/>
                  me alone with them<choice><orig/><reg>,</reg></choice><lb/>
                  and they scared the Boy<lb/>
                  away that was going<lb/>
                  to <choice><sic>marrie</sic><corr>marry</corr></choice> her so i<lb/>
                  <supplied reason="illegible" cert="medium">want</supplied> to take care of them<lb/>
                  <choice><sic>Becarse</sic><corr>because</corr></choice> they are mine<lb/>
                  and i will <choice><orig>all <supplied reason="omitted-in-original">ways</supplied></orig><reg>always</reg></choice> take care<lb/>
                  of them<choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice> She is a<supplied reason="omitted-in-original">t</supplied> <name type="place" subtype="address">1221<lb/>
                  madison</name> to <name type="person">mrs E. <choice><orig>Brown</orig><reg>Brown's</reg></choice></name><lb/>
                  house<choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice> Please go see her<choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice> <name>willie<lb/>
                     mae Ebron</name> is her name<choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice><lb/>
               </p>
            </div>
         <pb n="3" facs="../images/ew_b5_1652_003.jpg"/>
         <div>
            <head>5</head>
         <p>
            Please Let me <choice><sic>here</sic><corr>here</corr></choice><lb/>
            from ya at <supplied reason="illegible" cert="high">once</supplied><lb/>
            and <choice><sic>ablidge</sic><corr>oblige</corr></choice> me<choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice><lb/>
            my Daughter is <name type="person">Willie<lb/>
            mae Ebron</name> at <name type="place" subtype="address">1221<lb/>
               madison <choice><abbr>st</abbr><expan>street</expan></choice></name> <supplied reason="illegible" cert="medium"><choice><abbr>c/o</abbr><expan>care of</expan></choice></supplied> <name type="person">mrs<lb/>
            E. Brown</name><choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice><lb/>
            i am Looking for a <supplied reason="missing letters" cert="medium">Reply</supplied><lb/>
            from ya<choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice><lb/>
         </p>
            <closer>
               <signed><name type="person">Willie Ebron</name></signed><lb/>
               <name type="place" subtype="address">625 Liberty</name> <supplied reason="illegible" cert="medium"><choice><abbr>c/o</abbr><expan>care of</expan></choice></supplied><lb/>
               <del type="strikeout">Dul</del> Duval <choice><abbr>co.</abbr><expan>county</expan></choice> Jail
            </closer>
         </div>
         <pb/>
            <div>
               <note type="editorial">This following transcription is from the envelope that accompanies the letter.</note>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="left">
                     <name type="place" subtype="address">233 W.<lb/>
                        <supplied reason="illegible">Eagle</supplied> <choice><abbr>st</abbr><expan>street</expan></choice><lb/>
                        <supplied reason="illegible" cert="low"><abbr>chg</abbr></supplied> first <choice><abbr>st</abbr><expan>street</expan></choice><lb/>
                        <name type="place" subtype="city">Jacksonville</name> <choice><abbr>Fla</abbr><expan>Fla</expan></choice>
                     </name>
                  </hi>
                  <hi rend="center">
                     <name type="person"><choice><sic>Mis</sic><corr>Miss</corr></choice> <choice><abbr>E.</abbr><expan>Eartha</expan></choice> M. White</name><lb/>
                     <name type="place" subtype="address"># 233. W. first <choice><abbr>st</abbr><expan>street</expan></choice></name>
                  </hi>
                  <note place="marginRight"><choice><abbr>c/o.</abbr><expan>care of</expan></choice> <abbr>ctg.</abbr> <choice><sic>imployment</sic><corr>employment</corr></choice> <supplied reason="illegible" cert="low"><sic>Briror</sic></supplied></note>
               </p>
            </div>
      </body>
